Well, why not? We can use an extra pair of helping hands in the kitchen!
Bem, por que não? Podemos usar um par extra de ajudantes na cozinha!
~
CHEF_JOIN_3.TXT
Gee, I'd like to, but unfortunately I have run out of space in my kitchen! Perhaps next time...
